				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: 'Big Brother' Racist And Homophobic Comments Get Two Contestants Fired From Day J
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1786498">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							<div class="bbcode_container">
	<div class="bbcode_quote">
		<div class="quote_container">
			<div class="bbcode_quote_container"></div>
			
				<div class="bbcode_postedby">
					<img src="images/misc/quote_icon.png" alt="Quote" /> Originally Posted by <strong>Filan</strong>
					
				</div>
				<div class="message">This is a game show, Its a contest and its there to push people to their wits end for a global audience. people that lose jobs over what they say there? their employer is the party who is wrong.</div>
			
		</div>
	</div>
</div>There's three people who are over the top with this stuff: Aaryn (or Aryan, as people have started calling her), GinaMarie, and Spencer. Transcribed from Survivor Sucks:<br />
<br />
Aaryn<br />
&#8226;Re: Candice: Be careful what you say in the dark, you might not be able to see the bitch (6/30 ~7:45pm)<br />
&#8226;I want to put a washcloth over her face and pour water over it (6/30 7:42pm C1/2)<br />
